1. *Bol* se osećao u celom telu. (He felt pain throughout his body.)
2. On je u *bolu* plakao cijelu noć. (He was weeping in pain the whole night.)
3. U *bolu* je mislio na svoju porodicu. (He thought of his family in pain.)
4. Ona je sa *bolom* u glasu rekla da ne može dalje. (She said she couldn't go on with a pain in her voice.)
5. *Bole* su ga noge od prevelikog trčanja. (His legs were hurting from too much running.)